To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private LadderBottom _ladderbottom;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_ladderbottom = LadderBottom(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_ladderbottom.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "ladderbottom", _ladderbottom.Current.Value);
}
